events.name: She is a Leader (for Girls only)
events.description:
*_For Girls Only_*

She is A leader is a joint-event organized by TADFI English club & Women Tech-Makers Ghardaia in partnership with Nouzhal El Albab Club.
The event will be presented in a form of a session of coaching delivered by 5 young female coaches.
These sessions aim for the personal and professional development of our young women.
It is a chance for our young participants to share their ideas and learn new ones by asking and sharing.

- Women Startups
- Freelancing
- Motivation to get first step in her own business
- Futures (smart house/kitchen)
- Tech for kids ?
- Safety and security
- AR (augmented reality) / AI (artificial intelligence) Wearables / gadgets

events.name: Cloud Study Jam - Session 1
events.description:
Want to get started on the Google Cloud, but don't know where to begin?

Join us for our Cloud Study Jam!

Google Compute Engine lets you create and run virtual machines on Google infrastructure.it offers scale, performance, and value that allows you to easily launch large compute clusters on Google's infrastructure.

The session is 2 hours of interactive material and hands-on activities.

To get the best out of the session, consider the following Prerequisites:

This training assumes little to no prior knowledge in cloud computing or with the Google Cloud Platform. It is expected that students have an information technology or computing background, and have some hands-on familiarity with administering computing systems. Prior work with shell environments / command line interfaces will be helpful for completing the labs in this training. Also don't forget to

1.Bring your laptop: Mac, PC, Chromebook, Linux, everyone is welcome.
2. Computer charger
3. For a better experience in the laboratories, it is necessary to have main browser Firefox or Chrome
4. Limited seats are available
5. It is a FREE event
